      <p><span class="Section-Header">COVID-19 SCHOOL CLOSURE INFORMATION</span></p> 
      <p> </p> 
      <p>On Monday March 16, 2020 Governor Murphy ordered the indefinite closing of all state public, private and charter schools. This order may remain in effect past the Gray Charter School’s initial reopening date. Please monitor news reports in order to be informed as to when the Governor orders schools reopened. We will update our school website with this information as we receive it.  In the meantime, please remain healthy and take the proper steps to eliminate the spread of Covid-19. We look forward to seeing everyone back at school just as soon as this health crisis ends. Click the link below to read the official school announcement.</p> 
      <p> </p> 
