		<p><span class="Section-Header">April 20th Board Meeting Update</span>
		</p>
<p> </p>
<p>In response to the Covid-19 Pandemic, the next regularly scheduled meeting of the Gray Charter School's Board of Trustees will be conducted by teleconference. The meeting will take place on Monday April 20, 2020 at 5:00pm. Anyone wishing to attend the meeting should call 425.436.6326 and use Access Code: 881082. Thank you.</p>
		<p> </p>		
		
		
		<p><span class="Section-Header">Commissioner of Education Suspends all State Mandated Student Assessments</span>
		</p>
<p> </p>
<p>On Tuesday March 24, 2020 the Commissioner of Education suspended all state mandated student assessments for this school year. As a result, the New Jersey Student Learning Assessment which all of our students in grades 3-8 were scheduled to take from May 4 - May 18th of this year have been canceled. We will keep all parents updated as we receive additional information.</p>
